# --- Repo-root safety net (the real rules live in vyrex/.gitignore) ---

# Personal Claude Code / IDE tooling config — not a project deliverable.
.claude/

# Secrets — never publish (belt-and-suspenders; also ignored in vyrex/).
.env
**/.env
!**/.env.example

# Study-only reference clones (~1 GB, junctioned to D:). Never commit.
reference/
**/reference/
# Reference dashboard clone at the repo root (has its own .git) — study-only.
/ARIS-Security-Dashboard-main/

# Local k8s CLIs (kubectl / helm / k3d binaries) downloaded for the live-cluster tests.
.k8sbin/

# Build briefs / prompts kept local (not product deliverables).
/SOC-Central-ClaudeCode-Prompt.md
/SOC-Central-Tool-Integration-Prompt-2.md
/claude-code-prompt-soc-central-console.md

# Local data volumes / build artifacts / temp
**/data/
**/volumes/
__pycache__/
*.log
*.tmp
.git-commit-msg.tmp
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
